data.title: Punjabi / Sikh Wedding Dates 2024
data.meta_description: Filled with vibrant colours and divine celebration, a Punjabi wedding is a grand event. The wedding includes many detailed traditions, including Roka
data.text:
Filled with vibrant colours and divine celebration, a Punjabi wedding is a grand event. The wedding includes many detailed traditions, including Roka (engagement), Mehendi raat, and Anand Karaj, a ceremony for the newlyweds to take vows before the Guru Granth Sahib. A destination wedding in Punjab provides a joyous atmosphere and luxurious venues, with people celebrating through Bhangra dance, joyous Punjabi wedding music, and unique delicacies.

Interestingly, amid the many culturally significant traditions followed during a destination wedding in Punjab, one has many wedding duties, including selecting venues and choosing the right themes. However, before these steps, selecting the perfect wedding dates is the most necessary step for a beautiful destination wedding. And to help you with your big day duties, we have listed down the auspicious Punjabi wedding dates for the year 2024.

Auspicious Punjabi Wedding Dates in the month of January 2024:

The first month of the year can be great for a destination Punjabi wedding. With a temperature range of 0 to 18 degrees Celsius and 20 mm of precipitation, the month of January provides a great opportunity for a winter-themed wedding. You can select various colourful prints paired with the luxurious palette of Punjabi delicacies to add extra charm to your wedding day next year. According to the calendar, the month of January provides five wedding dates in the last half of the month for a big fat Punjabi wedding.

15 January 2024 (Sunday)

22nd January 2024 (Sunday)

24th January 2024 (Tuesday)

29th January 2024 (Sunday)

30th January 2024 (Monday)

Auspicious Punjabi Wedding Dates in the month of February 2024:

The most romantic month of the year, February, with a temperature range of 5 to 22 degrees Celsius and a rainfall predictability of 25 mm, can present a perfect platform for you to take your wedding vows. With several wedding dates fixed around Valentines Day, the month provides an opportunity to incorporate a love theme and play with different shades of red for your nuptials. You can also select cosy resorts or villas for comfortable weather in the morning and a cosy evening to cherish your love. According to the calendar, the month provides five wedding dates for a Punjabi-style destination romantic wedding.

5th February 2024 (Sunday)

7th February 2024 (Tuesday)

12th February 2024 (Sunday)

19 February 2024 (Sunday)

21st February 2024 (Tuesday)

Auspicious Punjabi Wedding Dates in the month of March 2024:

The month of March welcomes spring in Punjab, with a temperature ranging between 11 and 25 degrees Celsius and 43 mm of rainfall predictability. The month provides a great time to use bold floral themes and vibrant fabrics to celebrate your Punjabi wedding rituals. The month of March, with a comfortable temperature, also helps you select luxurious resorts in Amritsar and Jalandhar for an early spring wedding. According to the calendar, the month provides five wedding dates for a quaint destination wedding in Punjab.

The month provides a great platform for an outdoor wedding and to incorporate vibrant floral colors paired with Punjabi delicacies. Nonetheless, the months general temperature between 22 and 37 degrees Celsius and a rainfall average of 22 mm still make it ideal for an outdoor wedding in luxurious destinations in Ludhiana. You can also blend spring and summer themes with a punjabi twist to add a unique touch to your big day in the year 2024. According to the calendar, the month of May provides five days scattered all through the month to celebrate your love alongside your friends and family.

Auspicious Punjabi Wedding Dates in the Month of June 2024:

Welcoming the sunny days with a blast in the month of June provides the last opportunity for a sunny destination wedding in Punjab. The month with a temperature range of 26 to 39 degrees Celsius and 64 mm of rainfall is ideal for a cosy wedding on the farms or resorts of Amritsar. Bold summer patterns paired with summer delicacies and chilled lassi will definitely help you elevate your nuptials. According to the calendar, there are five days in the first half of June for a dream summer destination wedding in Punjab.

2nd June 2024 (Friday)

Auspicious Punjabi Wedding Dates in the months of July, August, September, and October 2024:

Unfortunately, according to the calendar, the months of July, August, September, and October do not provide any wedding dates in 2024. However, these four months with an average temperature range of 26 to 35 degrees Celsius and the highest predicted rainfall of 200mm in July will help you prepare for a dreamy winter wedding. You can complete your wedding shopping list, select venues, and spend some quality time with your loved ones before your big day in November.

An auspicious Punjabi wedding date in the month of November 2024:

Finally, after four months of a long hiatus, November is the perfect month to get married. With a temperature range of 9 to 27 degrees and 3 mm of rainfall predictability, the month helps you plan a cosy winter-themed wedding. Interestingly, you can pair warm or neutral colors while blending fall and winter aesthetics for your big day. The month can also create a great opportunity for comfortable weddings in the luxurious resorts of Punjab. According to the calendar, there are five days in the month for a destination wedding in Punjab.

3rd November 2024 (Saturday)

5th November 2024 (Monday)

Auspicious Punjabi Destination Wedding Dates in the month of December 2024:

Amid so many festivals, you can end your next year with a perfect winter-themed wedding. You can select a pure winter theme and different shades of white for your nuptials in the last month of the year. Amid many auspicious dates at the beginning of the month, you may also embark on a new journey while celebrating the arrival of the new year and the cherished festival of Christmas. According to the calendar, the month of December provides five wedding dates in the first half to end your last month auspiciously.

1st December 2024 (Friday)

6th December 2024 (Wednesday)

8th December 2024 (Friday)

13 December 2024 (Wednesday)

15th December 2024 (Friday)

In essence, the year 2024 provides various perfect dates in seven months to plan your big day. Intriguingly, these auspicious wedding days are scattered throughout different seasons for your nuptials. Now its time for you and your loved ones to show off their wedding skills and help plan your dream destination wedding in Punjab with the help of nuptial dates provided by us.
